Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.21,0:00:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hi, everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star, please \Nkeep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. Doesn't \Nit make you really anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}when you go somewhere you don't know?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.42,0:00:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I bump into \Nis something new for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Applying something I've already learned \Nor memorized is not good enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know it happens all the time, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I wonder why they still keep getting \Nmad at me?! I wonder. I wonder!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.99,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be someplace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has to be somewhere {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.53,0:01:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.25,0:01:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Remember how I used to say \NI could make it to the end?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I must have been pretending to be tough{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything I did was reckless \Nand it never got me anywhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.56,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you alone were always beside me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.95,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dream everyone is looking \Nfor must be somewhere{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.91,0:01:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You can start going forward {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.50,0:01:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From this moment, something will start{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe that {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:02:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The light I haven't seen yet is \Nbeaming toward the promised place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Until your dream comes true \Nsomeday, you're not alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.80,0:02:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we have a week, we can really relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once in a while, it would be nice \Nif we could travel or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.77,0:02:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're full of energy, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take a break and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.68,0:02:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like visiting a town \NI've never visited before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, just let loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? This is an airline ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you possibly be rewarding me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for my hard work with a trip somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Possibly? Possibly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.88,0:03:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dream came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, at least your dream came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.39,0:03:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to make a guest appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Work, work, work... I have to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in my old friend Mr. Pack's circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An ordeal...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The card signifies sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ominous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:50.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Mysterious Amazing Circus."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.26,0:03:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there, I will be your manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please expect me to act accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you're coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.51,0:04:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess life is good sometimes. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to a place \Ncalled Theatrical Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Theatrical Camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mobile circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their highlights are fire \Nbreathing, knife throwing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,whip tricks, and keg juggling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.24,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I also need to do fire breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.45,0:04:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.75,0:04:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have been waiting for \Nyou, Miss Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Theatrical Camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is breathing flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the audience is participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.49,0:05:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Milo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Tank!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.89,0:05:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the place quick once \Nyou finish your juggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it makes the kids happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.33,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come up with an excuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.86,0:06:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat the \Nsame thing over and over!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.17,0:06:05.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who ate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Excuse me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm introducing a guest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Miss Sora Naegino.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came from Kaleido Stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sora's manager, Ken Robbins.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This evening's beef stew has the best meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat, meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For tomorrow's show, since we have a guest,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.97,0:06:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't we do the one we \Nhaven't done in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Sora Naegino...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to play the \Nleading part, the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leading part?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.92,0:06:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the role of a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I'm capable \Nof playing that role.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.07,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, impossible, impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, impossible, impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.41,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story itself is very simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The role we want you to play
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is a heroine who rescues \Nher younger twin sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who are taken by a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mila and Milo are throwing \Naway carrots again, Dominique.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do it again, you'll have no dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pamela, you're going to \Nplay the villain, a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tank, you're going to play a glutton \Nwith supernatural strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will fight against a \Nknife-throwing monster man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you will head for the witch's nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pack, don't forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, Mr. Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the heroine's only ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them cooperate \Nto rescue the twins,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they fall in love and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lov--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.37,0:08:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It comes to a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they need to fall in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you feed him milk?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.10,0:08:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lion handler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:30.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuffed animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This script talks about the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it doesn't say anything \Nabout how we perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:36.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.07,0:08:38.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We already said that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask during rehearsal tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.24,0:08:40.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I should rest well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It already came up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it did {\i1}not{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came up, it came up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came up, it came up, it came up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.23,0:09:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the stars are beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? All of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you always help me \Nwhenever I'm in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you encourage me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.04,0:09:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt I would've had the chance \Nto play the Little Mermaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the chance to co-star \Nwith Miss Layla, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.87,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got those things because you worked hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.63,0:09:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.63,0:09:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a hard worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You work too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sometimes feel that you \Nmay end up out of my league.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should get some sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It's noisy and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll do my best and try to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that would be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.99,0:09:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I will do my best and sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.75,0:10:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That baby cried all night long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Tank's snoring was pretty bad too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.26,0:10:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The male cast isn't here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then what about the rehearsal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're probably not going to have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? They're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They almost never rehearse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what's everyone doing now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until the evening performance, \Nit's their free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's coming from the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.71,0:10:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what to \Ndo, since nobody was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet everyone went out to have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.41,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People in town give us a warm reception,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we get free food and drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't rehearse at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't perform without a rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... What shall I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I will teach \Nyou one important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.02,0:11:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you saw the show yesterday, \NI think you already know this,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:18.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but each member has something \Nthat they're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story itself is there just so \Neach of us can show off our forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So always pay attention to the \Naudience's reaction, and proceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed while paying attention \Nto the audience's reaction...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you want to show the \Naudience is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pamela!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.19,0:12:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to rescue your sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.87,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should come to my castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder, can I show up already? \NI wonder... I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.66,0:12:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a heroine. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.55,0:12:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So I have to act like one. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mila, Milo where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the witch didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't finished my lines yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like everything is going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going smoothly?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Beer kegs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is indeed the time to \Ntest the Princess's courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please... Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.03,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't finish the show like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not like this! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you people thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is how she's going to be treated,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll refuse to let her \Nappear on stage tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Miss Sora Naegino insists on that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems showing a new member in \Ntrouble is all part of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can explain the situation to Kalos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.54,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind them making fun of my mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all laughing at \Nme because I was a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.38,0:15:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday's show...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was amazing. The \Naudience and cast became one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.36,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today, from the beginning to the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they treated me like a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't even allow me to perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about Pamela?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Dio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible what Pamela did to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.53,0:15:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But did you notice Pamela \Nbefore you grabbed the swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.87,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stole Pamela's thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.58,0:15:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mr. Dio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to sleep already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for what I did to you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.82,0:16:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you feel like going back already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so easy that you'll get applause
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just for following the script \Nlike you do at Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage isn't that easy either!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not leaving yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.02,0:16:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.29,0:16:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I perform here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will appear on stage as \None of the members here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, tomorrow, please make sure to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a foolish person's upright position?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.77,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.19,0:16:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look upset after being tossed \Nabout in the storms of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come because you \Nwere worried about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.92,0:17:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I endured staying inside that tight suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.52,0:17:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected you to get so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.38,0:17:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I'm here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... A roach...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's start with \Nlearning more about the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.19,0:17:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected, the stage as a whole is small.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means there's not much distance \Nbetween you and the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, at Kaleido Stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the audience can't see the \Nperformers' subtle expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.77,0:17:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But here, the audience can see your \Nexpressions even when you're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doing the same show I do at Kaleido \NStage doesn't attract the audience here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.34,0:17:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to perform while observing \Nthe cast members and the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Unless I can do that, I can't be one of them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to rescue your sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should come to my castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mila, Milo, where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were they kidnapped by the witch?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.57,0:18:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make sure to rescue them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I miss something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here, here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, beer kegs!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.30,0:18:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora Naegino!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good, I think I can do this. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying to hit the \Nbull's-eye right in that circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will show you the leading role's maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What! Straight up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.74,0:20:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Miss Pamela!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen anything like that before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can manage that maneuver \Nonly one time in five.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.12,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't want to be outdone by you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great maneuver which may \Nhurt you isn't required here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing which is required here
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the ability to appear on stage every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaleido Stage isn't everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand very well that \Neach troupe has a show
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's best suited for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.73,0:20:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to be in Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it wasn't my kind of place, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't allowed to do what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.52,0:21:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like the kind who \Ndoes whatever you want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean to act that way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're just what Kaleido \NStage needs right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly though, it's the time to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Milo's twisted an ankle \Nduring today's performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's earlier than the date we had in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.60,0:21:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we decided to cut the performance short.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Olives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Pack plants olives like \Nthese at each place we camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his hobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.32,0:21:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that the olive, the symbol of peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can sprout the next season even if \Nthe place where it was burns down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to be as strong as this olive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.65,0:21:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the olive is a must-have for a good salad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That princess role was played by \Nmany people, including Pamela,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I thought she had such invaluable talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless someone nurtures her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the flower of her talents will never bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.31,0:22:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make sure to nurture her talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.98,0:22:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pamela, please come to see our show too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.65,0:22:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:36.75,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Next Kaleido Star"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.33,0:22:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm afraid he no longer needs me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.17,0:22:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so... {\i0}
